00:01:43.399 --> 00:01:44.759
some of the food for Bichen.

00:01:44.960 --> 00:01:46.839
No need to save any more for her.

00:01:46.960 --> 00:01:48.319
Mom, no need to save any for her.

00:01:48.440 --> 00:01:50.319
She's eating at her parents' today.

00:01:51.000 --> 00:01:52.440
She went to her mom's?

00:01:53.160 --> 00:01:54.440
Will she be back tonight?

00:01:54.440 --> 00:01:55.800
Yeah, I'll pick her up later.

00:02:00.880 --> 00:02:01.640
Dad, Mom.

00:02:02.919 --> 00:02:05.160
I want to discuss something.

00:02:06.039 --> 00:02:06.679
Go on.

00:02:07.559 --> 00:02:08.760
Chen's cultural center

00:02:08.760 --> 00:02:10.520
built a new center at Qianhu.

00:02:10.640 --> 00:02:11.559
They're short on staff.

00:02:12.119 --> 00:02:14.279
If she transfers, she gets promoted.

00:02:14.480 --> 00:02:15.839
They also give staff housing.

00:02:16.240 --> 00:02:17.599
Chen and I checked it out.

00:02:17.670 --> 00:02:18.960
An 80 square meter, two-bed unit.

00:02:18.960 --> 00:02:20.279
The environment is great.

00:02:20.279 --> 00:02:21.599
There's a lake and courts.

00:02:21.599 --> 00:02:23.240
Wait, Qianhu...

00:02:23.240 --> 00:02:24.879
Where on earth is that?

00:02:24.879 --> 00:02:25.999
Very far.

00:02:25.999 --> 00:02:27.559
A place no one goes to.

00:02:27.559 --> 00:02:28.879
Dad, you're exaggerating.

00:02:28.879 --> 00:02:30.119
There's a new highway.

00:02:30.279 --> 00:02:31.599
It's only 40 minutes.

00:02:31.999 --> 00:02:32.520
4...

00:02:32.520 --> 00:02:34.040
Is 40 minutes not far?

00:02:34.040 --> 00:02:35.879
Exactly, it's too far.

00:02:36.080 --> 00:02:36.640
You...

00:02:36.839 --> 00:02:37.640
Alright. Let me ask.

00:02:37.640 --> 00:02:39.640
Why are you telling us this?

00:02:40.240 --> 00:02:41.159
What do you mean?

00:02:42.119 --> 00:02:45.399
Chen said she wants to go.

00:02:46.320 --> 00:02:47.480
She wants to go. Chen...

00:02:47.920 --> 00:02:49.080
She's pregnant.

00:02:49.200 --> 00:02:50.879
It's not a problem.

00:02:50.960 --> 00:02:52.559
She's months from due date.

00:02:52.559 --> 00:02:53.719
Her boss said

00:02:53.719 --> 00:02:55.559
she'll get full maternity leave.

00:02:57.240 --> 00:02:58.240
