00:03:08.960 --> 00:03:10.439
She'll go shine.

00:03:10.439 --> 00:03:11.399
What about you?

00:03:11.559 --> 00:03:12.240
Exactly.

00:03:13.920 --> 00:03:15.240
I'll quit my job

00:03:15.399 --> 00:03:16.439
and go with her.

00:03:17.200 --> 00:03:18.760
Quit?

00:03:19.879 --> 00:03:20.999
How will you provide?

00:03:20.999 --> 00:03:22.119
Mom, let me finish.

00:03:22.119 --> 00:03:23.960
You're a grown man.

00:03:23.960 --> 00:03:25.279
You should provide.

00:03:25.320 --> 00:03:27.320
