00:03:30.080 --> 00:03:31.399
You can't support a family.

00:03:31.559 --> 00:03:32.879
But I'll have time.

00:03:32.960 --> 00:03:34.399
Chen and I agreed.

00:03:34.399 --> 00:03:35.800
After the baby comes,

00:03:35.800 --> 00:03:36.760
I'll raise them.

00:03:38.599 --> 00:03:41.640
