00:09:19.920 --> 00:09:21.200
But once I think of Jiao,

00:09:21.800 --> 00:09:22.920
I just can't do it.

00:09:23.800 --> 00:09:25.040
I managed to do it today.

00:09:26.239 --> 00:09:27.560
I'm not going back.

00:09:29.519 --> 00:09:30.160
Sure.

00:09:33.599 --> 00:09:34.479
Jiao.

00:09:34.920 --> 00:09:36.599
I'm out of town for work.

00:09:37.119 --> 00:09:39.639
Listen to Dad at home.

00:09:39.920 --> 00:09:41.479
Do your homework.

00:09:49.400 --> 00:09:50.800
I said I'm not going back.

00:09:51.800 --> 00:09:53.999
You keep turning your phone on and off.

00:09:53.999 --> 00:09:55.200
Aren't you tired?

00:09:55.200 --> 00:09:56.920
I'm worried about Jiao.

00:09:57.680 --> 00:09:58.800
I argued with Zhang Hao,

00:09:58.800 --> 00:10:00.599
but Jiao's my own child.

00:10:04.560 --> 00:10:05.160
Maodou.

00:10:05.920 --> 00:10:07.400
Look at this room.

00:10:07.920 --> 00:10:08.920
Isn't it nice?

00:10:09.440 --> 00:10:10.680
Isn't it fancy?

00:10:11.599 --> 00:10:12.680
Let me tell you.

00:10:12.920 --> 00:10:14.680
This bed is comfortable.

00:10:14.999 --> 00:10:15.599
Really.

00:10:15.759 --> 00:10:17.359
It's super soft.

00:10:18.800 --> 00:10:22.359
It's a waste for me to stay alone.

00:10:22.599 --> 00:10:24.200
That's why I asked you over for a bath.

00:10:24.440 --> 00:10:25.400
Still a waste.

00:10:25.400 --> 00:10:27.479
You should've invite
your whole family to bathe.

00:10:28.119 --> 00:10:29.920
Jiao loves taking baths.

00:10:30.440 --> 00:10:31.999
